description: ABSTRACT: The BOReal Ecosystem-Atmosphere Study (BOREAS) Terrestrial Ecology (TE)-11 team collected several data sets in support of its efforts to characterize and interpret information on the sapflow, gas exchange, and lichen photosynthesis of boreal vegetation and meteorological data of the area studied. This data set contains the meteorological data taken in the BOREAS Southern Study Area (SSA) during 1994 and used by TE-11 for their sapflow and gas exchange data analysis.
name: BOREAS TE-11 Surface Meteorological Data
